    "whatList": "• Discover famous places and attractions\n• Find restaurants, cafes, and local food spots\n• Explore public transportation options\n• Search and book flights\n• Rent apartments and accommodations\n• Build personal travel itineraries\n• Save places to your wishlist\n• Keep a personal travel journal",

